data.description:
Nestled in the heart of tranquil country living, this meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bath home provides the perfect blend of modern comfort and peaceful surroundings. With 1,566 square feet of living space and situated on a generous 0.78-acre lot, this property is a dream come true for those seeking a serene lifestyle.
Key Features:
Newly Remodeled Kitchen: Step into a chef's paradise with a freshly remodeled kitchen that
boasts all the modern amenities you desire. From gleaming countertops to updated fixtures,
this space is perfect for whipping up culinary masterpieces or enjoying everyday meals with
your loved ones.

Fresh Flooring & Paint: The entire interior of this home has been treated to fresh paint and
new flooring, providing a clean, welcoming ambiance. The updated aesthetics create a canvas
for your personal touch and style.

Spacious Bedrooms: Three generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for rest and
relaxation. Each room is designed with comfort in mind, ensuring peaceful nights and cozy
mornings.

Outdoor Oasis: Step outside into your very own outdoor oasis. The large front yard provides 
plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening. Perfect for kids, pets, and your green
thumb!

Outdoor Oasis: Step outside into your very own outdoor oasis. The large front yard provides
plenty of space for outdoor activities and gardening. Perfect for kids, pets, and your green
thumb!

Above Ground Pool: Beat the summer heat in your very own above-ground pool. It's an ideal
spot to relax, unwind, and entertain friends and family on warm, sunny days.

Chicken Coop: Embrace sustainable living with your very own chicken coop. Harvest fresh
eggs daily and enjoy the satisfaction of tending to your feathered friends.

Country Charm: The property exudes a timeless, country charm that's sure to captivate your
heart. Experience the tranquility of rural life while still being conveniently close to essential
amenities and services.

If you've been dreaming of a peaceful, countryside retreat with modern comforts and plenty
of outdoor space, this 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is the perfect opportunity. Don't miss your
chance to make this slice of paradise your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience
the serenity of country living at its finest.
